      <problem id="fs-id368027">  
        <para id="import-auto-id3119275">(a) How many <m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mtext>239</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mtext>Pu</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{ {} rSup { size 8{"239"} } "Pu"} {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math> nuclei must fission to produce a 20.0-kT yield, assuming 200 MeV per fission? (b) What is the mass of this much <m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mtext>239</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mtext>Pu</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{ {} rSup { size 8{"239"} } "Pu"} {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math>?</para>
